#

Truffle Risotto with Wild Mushrooms and Grilled Asparagus

$28.5
550 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyMushrooms

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

GourmetComfort FoodItalian

Description

A luxurious and creamy risotto infused with truffle oil, complemented by earthy wild mushrooms and perfectly grilled asparagus for a gourmet touch.

Ingredients

  • Arborio rice: 1 cup
  • Vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • Wild mushrooms (such as shiitake, oyster, and cremini): 2 cups, sliced
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch, trimmed
  • Shallots: 2, finely chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Parmesan cheese: 1/2 cup, grated
  • Truffle oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Fresh parsley: for garnish
